com.breeze.query

Class EntityQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.breeze.query.EntityQuery

  • public class EntityQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a query against a strongly typed model. This query is designed to be easily converted into variety of persistence library query languages via subclasses of the QueryProcessor class. An EntityQuery is an immutable structure. This means that mutation methods on an EntityQuery actually all return new EntityQuery instances.
    Author:
    IdeaBlade
